    "title": "Crossword Bookstores is Hiring: Floor Manager (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Floor Manager with drive and ambition, Crossword Bookstores in Tiruchirappalli is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Crossword Bookstores:\nCrossword Bookstores is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Crossword Bookstores!",
